title: First Love Cringe | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 18
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


This episode the Babes talk SAL'S GOT A NEW HAT, cliff hanger story continues, shout out everything, Someone broke into Sal's land lord's house and Sal is enlisted to help him chase the robber, Chris had a fire in his house as a kid, anyone else have wild anxiety about being pulled over by the police?, Chris' chain breaks and Sal investigates, why do men wear chains?, Sal whips out his childhood jewelry and puts on a fashion show, What do you BABES think of Sal's collection?, do you have stuff from the day you were born?, Chris dad surprises us with a loving moment that Chris ruins, love you vs i love you vs love ya, Chris' first kiss was WEIRD, love at first sight is BS, How long do you wait till saying I love you to a new partner?, Chris has texted with Jerry Seinfeld but has never watched the show, shout out George Costanza, roller coaster accidents, reality dating shows make no sense, first time Sal saw people french kissing changed his life, Sal tells the story about his first love and all the cringe things he did chasing the high of young love, the babes break into song, anyone else write love letters in their teenage years?


Rate us on iTunes! Follow us on social media @HeyBabePod
